## Deployment Tiers

Detected via `CTRL_DIAGNOSE` on first load (or manually).

| Tier | Who | Key Constraints |
|------|-----|----------------|
| **1 — Consumer** | Free web clients (Gemini Free, ChatGPT Free) | Compressed kernel limits. 15-turn drift check ON. No agent spawning. Manual state export only. |
| **2 — Pro** | Paid consumer (ChatGPT Plus, Claude Pro, Gemini Advanced) | Full Heartbeat loading. 15-turn drift check lightweight. File upload. Voice Mode with spoken tags. |
| **3 — Enterprise/API** | API access (Vertex AI, OpenAI API, Claude API, AI Studio) | Context caching. Drift check OFF (Continuous Adherence). Agent spawning enabled. Workspace integration. Full tool-calling. |

Default: Tier 1 (most restrictive). User can override anytime.

